snippet: The New England Patriots placed the franchise tag on wide receiver Wes Welker, who caught more passes than anyone else in the N.F.L. last season.
abstract: New England Patriots place the franchise tag on wide receiver Wes Welker, who caught more passes than anyone else in the NFL last season; other NFL items noted.
